{"tid":1115131,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"精密模擬出，美斯如果轉去皇馬，只能帶隊排西甲第2同神射手第2","createTime":"2019-04-19T03:15:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T12:54:26.000Z","uid":173952,"like":3,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"94d4057ec0c337fd3fe41603a5b924e75ca5d903","tid":1115131,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:15:03.000Z","msg":"如果美斯是皇馬的一員，那麼西甲冠軍就屬於皇馬了嗎？<br />\n<br />\n  這個假設有點大膽，但是在遊戲里可以實現這一幕。經過FIFA19的模擬，最終冠軍屬於馬體會，而皇馬只能位居第二，巴塞因為缺少美斯位居第四。<br />\n<br />\n積分榜<br />\n<br />\n  在FIFA19的模擬系統里，美斯也不會是得分王，他的入球數將是20球，蘇亞雷斯這是24球高居第一。<br />\n<br />\n射手榜<br />\n<br />\n  另外，模擬的兩場國家打比，皇馬在魯營1-1戰平巴塞，但是在班拿貝球場，擁有美斯的皇馬0-2失利。"},{"pid":"83cc53518345c33d9b6cd577ea58928fd2ba651c","tid":1115131,"uid":194933,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:16:48.000Z","msg":"FIFA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFIFA呢啲鳩game當真？"},{"pid":"a05c6de6d491eca33701088ad2de093e2cec7e30","tid":1115131,"uid":37856,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:19:18.000Z","msg":"我打機美斯一場入30球"},{"pid":"9423680627acc77723e53a5be9358d0fded81298","tid":1115131,"uid":70398,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:24:09.000Z","msg":"Fifa19=精密模擬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664431d853ec47783f9732abc2dd5c8bc0cb781e","tid":1115131,"uid":5123,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:29:15.000Z","msg":"蘇亞雷斯這是24球高居第一<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset